<p>You can use this solution:</p>

<pre><code>static List&lt;Integer&gt; convert(int input) {
    List&lt;Integer&gt; list = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();
    int counter = 1;
    while (input &gt; 0) {
        if (input % 2 == 1) list.add(counter);
        counter++;
        input /= 2;
    }
    return list;
}
</code></pre>

<p>It outputs:</p>

<pre><code>[2, 3]
[1, 2, 3]
[4]
</code></pre>
